</TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE>
</CENTER>

<H1>Interest and Income Taxes</H1><P>Changing your mortgage term can make a difference in not only the interest you pay, but your income taxes. A longer mortgage term can increase your income tax deduction. Take a look at the results below, to see how the different terms stack up.

<P>
